				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Killed Chief with a 40-50 group twice yesterday.<BR>
First time, a bunch of Avengers popped 5-10 seconds after killing the chief and wiped half our party very swiftly.  I somehow started to run with 4 or 5 of them on my tail, and made to Iceclad zone.  They were running at a speed VERY slightly slower than my sow, and then again, I hada straight forward sow, no wolf form / pack spirit / whatever.  The level 14 druid sow - maxed out speed.<BR>
<BR>
The second time, no Avengers popped, maybe because we killed the Chief a bit away from the fort.<BR>
<BR>
Avengers are incredibly tough and are there to prevent farming of course, which is great move on the Verant's side.<BR>
<BR>
Farming is making items worthless, and that's not something anyone would like to see in EQ.<BR>

