				Here's teh deal on the avengers'<BR>
<BR>
They SOMETIMES spawn when you kill the chief.<BR>
<BR>
They spawn in a random number from 1 to 8 or so.<BR>
<BR>
They SOMETIMES run at above sow speed. Sometimes they run normally.<BR>
<BR>
They won't attack the dwarf NPC's that I've seen. They just let htem beat on them till they're dead. Though this takes a LONG time. Another piece of advice, DO NOT bind right at the iceclad zone. You can very easily get caught in a horrible loop of death via them. Bind a way away from teh zone.
